@AmandaLeslie16 Hello, Amanda. We are sorry to hear about your missing baggage. Please use the link below to contact our baggage team via the WhatsApp channel. They will assist you further.
https://t.co/ByPyqeV2ad
Thank you.

@SrijanS84300805 Yes, Srijan. By presenting their student club digital card at check-in, students can receive a 10 kg or 1 piece complimentary baggage allowance on Qatar Airways flights.
If you require any clarifications, please feel free to DM us.
Thank you.

